sql:
SELECT DISTINCT country_code
FROM happiness_indicators
WHERE year = 2015;

SELECT AVG(score) AS average_happiness_score
FROM happiness_indicators
WHERE country_code = 'ISL';

SELECT MAX(score) AS max_happiness_score
FROM happiness_indicators
WHERE year = 2015;

external_knowledge:
- "Happiest in the world" refers to countries with the highest average happiness scores; 
- "Trusted source" refers to a data source with a data_source_id of 1, implying a reliable or primary source of happiness score data; 
- Locations include the country name, continent, and region.

